data.description: MOSTLY RENOVATED 3BR/2BA IN SOUGHT AFTER N'HOOD! IMPOSSIBLE TO find a Stepless “Ranch-Like” End Unit Townhome in SUCH AN EXCEPTIONAL Community! Bright & Open Floorplan with Vaulted Ceiling in Great Room w/Gas Fireplace!! Beautiful New FLOORING & PAINT THROUGHOUT!  NEW FIXTURES, NEW ROOF & GARAGE DOOR!! LEVEL DRIVEWAY W/TWO CAR GARAGE & Ample Guest Parking!! FHA APPROVED! Don’t miss this Opportunity to live in a community with AMENITIES featuring Pool, Fitness Room,Clubhouse and low HOA fees! So close to Downtown Snellville – & if you haven’t heard about all the Shops, Dining, Events & Parks –A vibrant array of activities just waiting for you to explore! Very near The Grove at Towne Center, Snellville Farmer’s Market – a couple worth mentioning. Just minutes to I-78. Nestled in a private enclave within the community, this residence features a 2 CAR GARAGE and ample guest parking! The Well-designed floorplan highlights a spacious Laundry room conveniently situated off of the Garage.  Abundant Natural Light throughout; in the Large Master Bedroom feat. Generous Walk-in Closet & Vaulted Ceiling! FORMAL dining room complimented by a generously sized Open Kitchen feat. Bar Seating & abundant Cabinet Space! Quiet well managed community with low HOA fees  covering lawn maintenance! Two Secondary Bedrooms adjoined by a Jack & Jill Bath provide ample  space for guests or an Office! The serene ambience extends to the outdoors with OPEN uncongested  feel to each building with parking behind the units. Quiet GREENSPACE beside and behind this Townhome!   community with unparalleled comfortable & convenient living! Front photos only because seller is moving this week.
